public RoomProvidesFeature setFeature(Feature value)
Sets the value of feature. If the new value is the same as the old value, this method has no effect, i.e. if you specify a new value, than isFeatureChanged() will return true. If you specify the same value as the old value isFeatureChanged() will return the same as it did before calling setFeature(...).
